Setup the Alexa Skill to control your Viro Smart Lights:
1. Download the Viro App and set up your account;
2. In the Viro App, add a Viro Smart Light and rename it. You’ll use this name to tell Alexa commands;
3. In the Alexa App search Skills for the Viro Skill;
4. Enable the Viro Skill and enter your Viro App login details;
5. Follow the on-screen instructions to complete the setup;
You can now use Alexa to control your Viro Smart Light, try out commands like:
Alexa, Turn on “Name”
Alexa, Turn off “Name”
Alexa, Turn “Name” 50%
Alexa, Turn “Name” Warm
Alexa, Turn “Name” White
